Dremio Apache Pinot Connector
Community connector — Apache License 2.0

This product includes the following third-party software:

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Apache Pinot JDBC Driver
  Artifact:  org.apache.pinot:pinot-jdbc-client
  Version:   1.4.0
  License:   Apache License 2.0
  Source:    https://github.com/apache/pinot

  The Pinot JDBC driver is bundled in the plugin JAR (two-JAR deploy:
  plugin JAR + driver JAR placed in /opt/dremio/jars/3rdparty/).

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Dremio Sabot Kernel and Plugin API
  Artifact:  com.dremio:dremio-sabot-kernel (compile-time only)
  License:   Apache License 2.0
  Source:    https://github.com/dremio/dremio-oss

  Note: Dremio JARs are used at compile time only and are not bundled
  in the connector distribution. They must be present in the target
  Dremio installation.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Dremio ARP (Abstract Relational Plugin) Framework
  Artifact:  com.dremio:dremio-connector (compile-time only)
  License:   Apache License 2.0
  Source:    https://github.com/dremio/dremio-oss

  The connector uses Dremio's ARP/JDBC framework defined in
  pinot-arp.yaml for SQL dialect and pushdown configuration.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Apache Arrow
  Artifact:  org.apache.arrow:arrow-vector (compile-time only)
  License:   Apache License 2.0
  Source:    https://github.com/apache/arrow
